ing and sound systems will dazzle those both inside and out. Our library of over 75 games is sure to satisfy any crowd. And our staff is professionally trained and screened to ensure safety with your young guests. Let us take your next event to a whole new level. Join the Revolution and click now to book Mobile Gaming Revolution today!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:518:"<h4>Serving the Greater Seattle/Tacoma area</h4>\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://mgrparty.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20140118_111152332.jpg"  width=600px; >\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<div class="contact-details">\r\n<p>Dan Mitchell</p>\r\n<p>Phone: 1-855-GAMERZZ</p>\r\n<p>Email: <a href="mailto:seattle@mgrparty.com">seattle@mgrparty.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class="big">Feel free to give us a call with any questions you may have. We''re here to help make your event a success. Get in touch today and get the party started!</p>\r\n\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:292:"<h4>Serving All of Tampa Bay</h4>\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://mgrparty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/CORPORATE_PICTURE.jpg" width=600px>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<div class="contact-details">\r\n\r\n<p>Phone: 813-965-7449</p>\r\n<p>Email: <a href="mailto:Info@MGRparty.com">Info@MGRparty.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
