(1182, 318, 'revolutionary_name', 'Amy Call'),
(1183, 318, '_revolutionary_name', 'field_531072ed0e85c'),
(1184, 318, 'designation', 'Vp, Group Account Director'),
(1185, 318, '_designation', 'field_53107092b8b1f'),
(1186, 318, 'work', 'Amy is our VP, Group Account Director and Strategy Director. Prior to joining BLITZ she was a strategic lead at 180 and held the title of Director, Brand Leadership at Chiat Day/Tequila. With a record of consistent, high-profile successes for the likes of Gatorade, Visa, Mitsubishi Motors, Boost Mobile and many more, Amy brings a wealth of strategic and branding insight to BLITZ. And, since our office is located in walking distance from Nekter (her favorite juice bar), she routinely brings us Acai Banana Berry Bowls, too. Sweet.'),
(1187, 318, '_work', 'field_531070c4b8b20'),
(1188, 318, 'life', 'Amy lives life by the numbers. She’s traveled to 128 countries, filled four passports, and sailed all of the seven seas. Literally. Like in an actual sailboat and everything. She’s climbed 16,990 feet of the 29,029 feet of Mt. Everest, summited all of the 19,341 feet of Mount Kilimanjaro and ran and cycled thousands of miles. Amy eventually settled down here in Los Angeles near sea level, with eight fish, two starfish, two dogs and one seemingly depressed tadpole who, for some reason flat out refuses to become a frog. Amy’s number one favorite thing in the whole world? Her son.'),
(1189, 318, '_life', 'field_531071aeb8b21'),
