(1213, 322, '_designation', 'field_53107092b8b1f'),
(1214, 322, 'work', 'Peter Brine is a group account director, the role he was born to play. He loves being a part-time cheerleader, strategist, project manager, creative, critic, tester and full-time client advocate.  He''s not happy unless the client’s happy.'),
(1215, 322, '_work', 'field_531070c4b8b20'),
(1216, 322, 'life', 'Peter grew up in New England and slowly made his way south and west, picking up a B.A. degree from Georgetown and a law degree from the University of Georgia. He eventually ended up in L.A. and hasn’t left since.  When not at work, you can find him cooking at home with his wife, camping with his son''s Cub Scout Pack or playing Assassin''s Creed Revelations with his daughter.'),
