(52, 1, '2014-02-18 10:11:27', '2014-02-18 10:11:27', '<p>Are you sick of spending your post-party Saturday afternoon picking Nerf bullets out of your pool and spent water balloons from your Begonias? Did your son refuse to speak to you for a week after Uncle Ed showed up dressed like Bozo the Clown as a surprise for his fourteenth birthday party? Is your daughter’s Sweet Sixteen a huge conundrum because she’d rather wield a controller than a corsage? RELAX, we’ve got you covered. Make your kid’s party the event of a lifetime with this hot new trend: Gaming parties on the spot! Imagine a self-contained video gaming utopia, complete with XBOX 360, PlayStation 3, and Nintendo Wii all in a fully equipped, temperature controlled Mobile Video Gaming Theater. Sit back and relax while our highly trained staff takes care of everything. From Assassin’s Creed to Just Dance 4, Mobile Gaming Revolution has all the hottest, newest multiplayer games played on high definition flat screen TV’s, all while nestling your rump in state of the art gaming chairs. As if that’s not enough, top off the whole package with outdoor laser tag!</p>\r\n<p>Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash! <a href="http://mgrparty.com/contact/" target="_blank">Send us a message</a> now and let’s get this party started!</p>\r\n', 'Birthday Parties', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'birthday-parties', '', '', '2014-02-19 08:37:32', '2014-02-19 08:37:32', '', 0, 'http://sushovon/MGRparty/?post_type=events&#038;p=52', 0, 'events', '', 0),
