(98, 1, '2014-02-18 13:45:59', '2014-02-18 13:45:59', '<p>At Mobile Gaming Revolution , it’s “The Experience” that makes the difference.</p>\r\n<p>What makes it an “Experience”? Simply put, our staff, our equipment and our professionalism.</p>\r\n<p>Our friendly, highly-trained staff will be on-hand throughout your event to ensure that everything runs smoothly in a fun, engaging way. We truly love what we do, and it shows! We don’t simply run parties, we help to make memories!</p>\r\n<p>We are confident enough to say that our equipment is the best in the business! No boring, bare-wall, white-light video game theaters here! Our theaters are custom-designed with state-of-the-art sound and lighting systems that will surely give you and your guests the all-important “Wow” factor! </p>\r\n<p>At Mobile Gaming Revolution , professionalism is paramount. From the person handling phone calls and scheduling to the game coaches running your event, we promise to maintain a professional attitude at all times. Our customers always come first!</p>\r\n<p>Give us a call today to schedule your very own “MGR Experience”!</p>\r\n<h2>Test</h2>\r\n<p>At Mobile Gaming Revolution , professionalism is paramount. From the person handling phone calls and scheduling to the game coaches running your event, we promise to maintain a professional attitude at all times. Our customers always come first!</p>\r\n<p>Give us a call today to schedule your very own “MGR Experience”!</p>\r\n<h3>Test</h3>\r\n<p>At Mobile Gaming Revolution , professionalism is paramount. From the person handling phone calls and scheduling to the game coaches running your event, we promise to maintain a professional attitude at all times. Our customers always come first!</p>\r\n<p>Give us a call today to schedule your very own “MGR Experience”!</p>\r\n', 'The Experience', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-experience', '', '', '2014-02-27 09:16:54', '2014-02-27 09:16:54', '', 0, 'http://sushovon/MGRparty/?page_id=98', 0, 