(185, 1, '2014-02-19 08:39:22', '2014-02-19 08:39:22', '<p>Want to avoid donning your itty bitty Speedo for the annual Marching Band Car Wash? Why not catch people’s attention with something other than your swimsuit and a soapy bucket? (Dude, nobody wants to see that anyway.) Partner up with the fundraiser that creates its own buzz! Mobile Gaming Revolution is more than just a gamers’ utopia on wheels. It’s BIG! It’s LOUD! It draws a CROWD! Your donors will experience the thrill of our HD gaming theater and professional sound system while you reach your fund-raising goal with almost no effort. Sit back, relax, put away your suntan lotion… we’ve got all your parts covered.</p>\r\n<p>Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash! <a href="http://mgrparty.com/contact/" target="_blank">Send us a message</a> now and let’s get this party started!</p>\r\n', 'Schools, Fundraisers and Non-Profits', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'schools-fundraisers-and-non-profits', '', '', '2014-02-19 08:39:22', '2014-02-19 08:39:22', '', 0, 'http://sushovon/MGRparty/?post_type=events&#038;p=185', 0, 'events', '', 0),
(186, 1, '2014-02-19 09:24:46', '2014-02-19 09:24:46', '<p>So, are you totally bummed that you just celebrated your birthday at Uncle Hank’s House of Handicrafts instead of with a totally sweet Mobile Gaming Revolution gamers extravaganza? Don’t worry, sad little buddy, there a zillion reasons to celebrate! Our mobile gaming theater is perfect for:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bat Mitzvahs</li>\r\n<li>Bachelor Parties</li>\r\n<li>Tailgate Parties</li>\r\n<li>Family Reunions</li>\r\n<li>Company Picnics</li>\r\n<li>Sports Team End of Season Parties</li>\r\n<li>School Spirit Events</li>\r\n<li>Video Game Tournaments</li>\r\n<li>Scouting Events</li>\r\n<li>Mom’s/ Girls Night Out</li>\r\n<li>Dad’s/ Guys Night Out</li>\r\n<li>Anniversary Parties</li>\r\n<li>Super Bowl Parties</li>\r\n<li>Graduation Parties</li>\r\n<li>Surprise- I Got Straight-A’s Parties!</li>\r\n<li>New Year’s Eve</li>\r\n<li>Holiday Parties</li>\r\n<li>Back to School Events</li>\r\n<li>School’s Out for Summer Events</li>\r\n<li>“Just Because” Parties</li>\r\n<li>…and much, much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You can pretty much celebrate anything with Mobile Gaming Revolution’s HUGE flat screen TV’s, kickin’ sound and lighting system, and totally sweet interactive gaming hookups. Our climate-controlled gaming theater makes the weather outside a non-issue… Through rain, sleet, snow, wind, blistering sun or bitter cold, let the Nation’s PREMIER mobile entertainment company make your party a blast! Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash!</p>', 'Bar/Bat Mitzvah', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'barbat-mitzvah', '', '', '2014-03-04 05:15:20', '2014-03-04 05:15:20', '', 0, 'http://sushovon/MGRparty/?post_type=events&#038;p=186', 0, 'events', '', 0),
