(242, 1, '2014-02-25 07:51:30', '2014-02-25 07:51:30', '<p>Mobile Gaming Revolution was born in the first quarter of 2011 when we, three siblings, shared the vision of an awesome alternative to the traditional birthday party. Roller skating, inflatables, bowling, and laser tag were starting to fall behind the highly stimulating environment surrounding the children of this generation. It became our mission to amp up the party, and make it mobile. Our idea ended up bringing incredible experiences to tons of kids all over, but it also pulled us closer together as a family.</p>\r\n<p>The Mobile Gaming concept quickly became wildly popular, and not just with the kids. We moved into the world of corporate events, family reunions, carnivals, schools, grand openings, team-building events, and even fundraisers. In fact, at Mobile Gaming Revolution , we actively seek out charitable organizations and causes as a way to give back to our community.</p>\r\n<p>The future of our little family venture is now bigger than we could have ever imagined, so in the summer of ’12 we started franchising throughout the United States. Our company is comprised of young, energetic, easygoing, but hardworking people who share our mission and vision… to provide cutting edge entertainment that people will never forget.</p>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '106-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-25 07:51:30', '2014-02-25 07:51:30', '', 106, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/106-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(243, 1, '2014-02-25 13:41:38', '2014-02-25 13:41:38', '<ol>\r\n<li> <span>Check out our website and learn what we do. We''re perfect for virtually any event that is looking to add fun and excitement for all ages with our Gaming Theaters and high tech Laser Tag setup.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Call our party experts at 1-855-9-GameOn to discuss your event or request more information. Our experts make it fun and simple to get your party going.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Now relax, we''ve got the party covered from here. We show up on time, set up everything, and make sure you and your guests have the time of their lives!</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'HOW IT WORKS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-it-works', '', '', '2014-03-05 12:53:41', '2014-03-05 12:53:41', '', 0, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/?page_id=243', 0, 'page', '', 0),
