(268, 1, '2014-02-27 12:09:13', '2014-02-27 12:09:13', '<p>Are you sick of spending your post-party Saturday afternoon picking Nerf bullets out of your pool and spent water balloons from your Begonias? Did your son refuse to speak to you for a week after Uncle Ed showed up dressed like Bozo the Clown as a surprise for his fourteenth birthday party? Is your daughter’s Sweet Sixteen a huge conundrum because she’d rather wield a controller than a corsage?</p>\r\n<p>RELAX, we’ve got you covered. We make Birthday parties EASY for parents and FUN for kids!</p>\r\n<p>Make your next birthday party the event of a lifetime with the Nation’s PREMIER mobile entertainment company. Gaming parties on the spot! Imagine a self-contained video gaming utopia, complete with today’s HOTTEST gaming consoles all in a fully equipped, temperature controlled Mobile Video Gaming Theater. Sit back and relax while our highly trained staff takes care of everything. From Assassin’s Creed to Just Dance 4, Mobile Gaming Revolution has all the hottest, newest multiplayer games played on high definition flat screen TV’s, all while nestling your rump in the comfiest seating around.</p>\r\n<p>As if that’s not enough, top off the whole package with outdoor laser tag!<br />\r\nMobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash!</p>\r\n', 'Birthday Parties', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'birthday-parties', '', '', '2014-03-05 13:12:39', '2014-03-05 13:12:39', '', 0, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/?post_type=parties&#038;p=268', 0, 'parties', '', 0),
(269, 1, '2014-02-27 12:10:17', '2014-02-27 12:10:17', '<p>Want to avoid donning your itty bitty Speedo for the annual Marching Band Car Wash? Why not catch people’s attention with something other than your swimsuit and a soapy bucket? (Dude, nobody wants to see that anyway.) Partner up with the fundraiser that creates its own buzz! The Nation’s PREMIER mobile entertainment company, Mobile Gaming Revolution is more than just a gamers’ utopia on wheels. It’s BIG! It’s LOUD! It draws a CROWD! Your donors will experience the thrill of our HD gaming theater and professional sound system while you reach your fund-raising goal with almost no effort. Sit back, relax, put away your suntan lotion… we’ve got all your parts covered.</p>\r\n<p>Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash!</p>\r\n', 'Fundraisers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fundraisers', '', '', '2014-03-05 12:55:31', '2014-03-05 12:55:31', '', 0, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/?post_type=parties&#038;p=269', 0, 'parties', '', 0),
(270, 1, '2014-02-27 12:11:24', '2014-02-27 12:11:24', '<p>You’ve worked your fingers to the bone helping your business achieve a goal, reach a milestone, or finally launch the product that’s going to change the world as we know it! Or maybe you know you can get there, but you just don’t think rope burns or bean bag toss will help your staff take the “I” out of “team.” You don’t need your celebration of success or corporate team building event to be one more exhausting chore. Let the Nation’s PREMIER mobile entertainment company, Mobile Gaming Revolution do the work, and give your employees the kind of treatment they deserve! Our mobile gaming theater comfortably accommodates up to 28 highly valued coworkers at a time. With an indoor gaming oasis, and specially mounted exterior TV’s with interactive game systems, even that guy in accounting who grew up in the pre-Pong era will catch on quickly and have the time of his life!</p>\r\n<p>Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash!</p>\r\n', 'Corporate Parties', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'corporate-parties', '', '', '2014-03-05 13:03:33', '2014-03-05 13:03:33', '', 0, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/?post_type=parties&#038;p=270', 0, 'parties', '', 0),
(271, 1, '2014-02-27 12:12:35', '2014-02-27 12:12:35', '<p>So, are you totally bummed that you just celebrated your birthday at Uncle Hank’s House of Handicrafts instead of with a totally sweet Mobile Gaming Revolution gamers extravaganza? Don’t worry, sad little buddy, there a zillion reasons to celebrate! Our mobile gaming theater is perfect for:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bat Mitzvahs</li>\r\n<li>Bachelor Parties</li>\r\n<li>Tailgate Parties</li>\r\n<li>Family Reunions</li>\r\n<li>Company Picnics</li>\r\n<li>Sports Team End of Season Parties</li>\r\n<li>School Spirit Events</li>\r\n<li>Video Game Tournaments</li>\r\n<li>Scouting Events</li>\r\n<li>Mom’s/ Girls Night Out</li>\r\n<li>Dad’s/ Guys Night Out</li>\r\n<li>Anniversary Parties</li>\r\n<li>Super Bowl Parties</li>\r\n<li>Graduation Parties</li>\r\n<li>Surprise- I Got Straight-A’s Parties!</li>\r\n<li>New Year’s Eve</li>\r\n<li>Holiday Parties</li>\r\n<li>Back to School Events</li>\r\n<li>School’s Out for Summer Events</li>\r\n<li>“Just Because” Parties</li>\r\n<li>…and much, much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You can pretty much celebrate anything with Mobile Gaming Revolution’s HUGE flat screen TV’s, kickin’ sound and lighting system, and totally sweet interactive gaming hookups. Our climate-controlled gaming theater makes the weather outside a non-issue… Through rain, sleet, snow, wind, blistering sun or bitter cold, let the Nation’s PREMIER mobile entertainment company make your party a blast! Mobile Gaming Revolution brings you and your guests a thrilling on-location gaming experience designed to blow anything else out of the water! Whether you’re entertaining a dozen people or hundreds, we have options to meet your needs and your budget. FUN without the frazzle, we’re the experts at making your event a smash!</p>\r\n', 'Many more Parties', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'many-more-parties', '', '', '2014-03-05 13:05:30', '2014-03-05 13:05:30', '', 0, 'http://mgrparty.viewthedemo.com/?post_type=parties&#038